The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for improving search queries, which are common topics in the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural networks (cs.NE). The use of neural machine translation models also suggests a focus on deep learning techniques, which are commonly used in these sub-fields.
